# The site build only needs web/. Everything here is either enormous (data/raw
# is 2.4 GB of source PDFs, data/parquet ~250 MB) or irrelevant: the site reads
# precomputed JSON from web/src/data and never touches the Python side.
#
# Leading slashes anchor to the repo root. Without them, `src/` also matches
# `web/src/` and deletes the Next.js app directory out from under the build.
/data/
/.venv/
/notebooks/
/scripts/
/src/
/tests/
/inference_service/
/logs/
/migrations/
